::: def-title
Alternative / Larger / Full model
:::

::: def-cont
$\begin{aligned}Y = &\beta_0 + \beta_1 X_1 + \beta_2 X_2 + \beta_j X_j +\\ &\ldots + \beta_k X_k + \epsilon \end{aligned}$
